Streaming Tweets
The server receieves tweets from the Twitter Streaming API and pushes them to long polling clients. 

Requirements:
* node.js (tested with v0.1.30)

To Run:
* update twittercred.js with your Twitter credentials
* node server.js <optional_keyword>

Inspired by and based on:
* node_chat: http://github.com/ry/node_chat
* twitter-nodejs-websocket: http://github.com/andregoncalves/twitter-nodejs-websocket
